WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.230
Right. All right. Good morning, family. Good

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.670
evening, family, wherever you are. Thank

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:09.430
you for joining us again tonight. Well,

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:12.710
today the decision came out, didn't it?

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.550
I thought about it a lot

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.830
before I started to make this video and

00:00:18.840 --> 00:00:21.190
what I would say and how we were

00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:24.230
going to pray over our nation and

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:26.230
President Trump. Now,

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:28.470
I believe the Supreme Court missed

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:29.630
it big.

00:00:32.599 --> 00:00:34.990
But that's the way it all

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.190
works.

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:40.910
I was shocked. As much

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:43.550
prayer as we've all put into

00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:43.560
this—praying

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.590
for our nation and praying

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:49.070
for the Supreme Court's

00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:51.870
decision today. And so we

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.750
pray for President Trump. I know he's

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:57.030
very disappointed, probably very

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:58.190
angry.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:00.870
I wouldn't want to be

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:04.390
a fly on the wall in that Oval Office

00:01:04.390 --> 00:01:04.400
because

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:06.710
sometimes he has a foul mouth,

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:09.390
and so probably some strong words going

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:12.910
on in there.

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:14.350
But

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:16.150
so what do we do now?

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:17.870
That's where I was at tonight. Lord,

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:20.470
what now? The

00:01:20.470 --> 00:01:20.480
sky is

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:23.150
not falling, Chicken Little,

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:27.590
as he releases the alien files

00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:30.830
and tells everybody about the aliens and

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:34.070
says Obama leaked classified stuff and

00:01:34.080 --> 00:01:36.390
the things that were said over the last

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.950
couple of days.

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:44.310
I thought that's kind of interesting.

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:46.910
If we go back to what the Lord showed

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:47.910
us

00:01:47.910 --> 00:01:47.920
in

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.670
the

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:51.790
last video,

00:01:51.800 --> 00:01:53.630
I'm going to go over some of the visions

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:56.190
and what the Lord showed us in prayer,

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:58.190
and it lined up exactly with what

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.790
happened today.

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:02.430
Braden can play that clip real quick

00:02:02.440 --> 00:02:04.630
so we can get it over with.

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:10.870
On December 19th, I gave a

00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:13.710
pretty strong word about the economy and

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:16.190
what happens if the tariffs

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:19.350
don't happen the way I saw it. Does that

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.590
happen overnight?

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:23.510
I don't believe so.

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:26.870
I believe it's a gradual

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:29.470
fade.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:31.910
I believe with all my heart

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:34.070
we're so close to the coming of the Lord

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:36.310
Jesus Christ. Now, there's a lot of

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.030
people who believe we have

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:41.030
years and years left. I don't.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:43.230
When the Lord says, 'I'm coming and I'm

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:43.240
standing

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:44.750
at the door. I'm

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:47.550
waiting for the

00:02:47.550 --> 00:02:47.560
harvest.'When

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:50.670
I was with Him in tribulation,

00:02:50.680 --> 00:02:53.230
I saw the revival that took place.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:55.110
He showed me the last outpouring. He

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.550
showed me the spots. There were

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:00.390
golden spots all throughout the land

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.630
that represented souls and

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:05.229
the revival that was about to take

00:03:05.239 --> 00:03:07.350
place. And I saw Jesus when He

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:09.070
looked at Asia and the underground church,

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:11.190
and there were gold veins all throughout

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:13.750
Asia and all this was about to take

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:15.150
place

00:03:15.160 --> 00:03:18.550
was a major harvest.

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:20.229
Many people have asked me, 'How long do

00:03:20.239 --> 00:03:22.670
you think the revival lasts,

00:03:22.670 --> 00:03:22.680
Brandon?'I

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:26.070
said everything that I have seen in

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:27.870
the visions that the Lord

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:29.350
gives me

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:32.590
doesn't last very long—six months

00:03:32.600 --> 00:03:34.949
to a year at the most.

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:38.150
When we see the glorious outpouring on

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:40.229
the body of Christ

00:03:40.239 --> 00:03:43.070
with this last hurrah as this firework,

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:44.910
the grand finale of all

00:03:44.920 --> 00:03:47.310
firework shows, if you want to call it,

00:03:47.320 --> 00:03:50.110
and we're all operating in this

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:53.150
glorious outpouring. It doesn't take

00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:54.310
much

00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:56.710
when you start to see the dead raised

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:59.710
and the blind eyes open and

00:03:59.720 --> 00:04:01.910
creative miracles. Not just miracles of

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.030
saying, 'Well, Sister So-and-So had a

00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:05.470
headache and she got healed of a

00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:05.480
headache.'I'm

00:04:05.480 --> 00:04:08.550
talking undeniable

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:10.230
miracles.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.830
It's not going to take very many of

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.870
those to see a lot of people come in out

00:04:13.880 --> 00:04:16.349
of curiosity to say, 'What's going

00:04:16.349 --> 00:04:16.359
on?'And

00:04:16.359 --> 00:04:18.270
when you walk underneath that glory

00:04:18.280 --> 00:04:20.910
dome, the power of God hits everybody.

00:04:20.920 --> 00:04:22.390
Is everything okay?

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:25.270
The power of God hits everybody

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:28.390
and you're lying before a holy God

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:30.590
crying out for repentance. It's a

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:33.710
revival of repentance. It's a revival of

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:34.909
holiness.

00:04:34.919 --> 00:04:37.870
It's to come unto Him.

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.230
This is the end of the end.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:43.550
So everything that I have seen about

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:45.870
this revival comes out of great

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:47.909
pressure.

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:51.230
It doesn't come out of good times.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:53.710
Everything I've seen, it comes out of an

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:55.550
olive press

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:58.030
with persecution from the world.

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.430
Anti-Semitism rising at an all-time

00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:04.230
high. I see a lot

00:05:04.240 --> 00:05:06.750
about the revival, but everything that I

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:12.230
see leading up to it is not good.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:14.190
The Lord talked about a financial

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:17.870
blessing coming out of certain cryptos

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:20.830
and things like that that would fund

00:05:20.840 --> 00:05:23.430
this revival.

00:05:24.840 --> 00:05:26.710
Now, does God need finances to have a

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:29.550
revival?

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:33.350
Does God need a select few

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:35.030
people

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.630
to have millions of dollars to have a

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:38.909
revival?

00:05:38.919 --> 00:05:40.310
No.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:42.550
He did it with His disciples and

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:45.510
there were 12 of them plus the others,

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:48.310
and they changed the world with hardly nothing.

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:52.430
They were on foot.

00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:54.310
They traveled by boat

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:56.350
and look what they did with what

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:58.150
they had.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:59.550
You know what they had?

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.790
The glory.

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:02.350
They had the Holy Ghost and fire on

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:03.870
them.

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:05.870
And whenever you lay hands on people and

00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:07.470
you see them recover

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:11.190
and people are bound

00:06:13.240 --> 00:06:15.310
for so long and you see somebody like my

00:06:15.320 --> 00:06:17.270
daughter Megan start talking by the

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:19.270
power of God

00:06:19.270 --> 00:06:19.280
and

00:06:19.280 --> 00:06:20.790
she comes on here and starts telling you

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:22.990
about how Jesus is so wonderful and how

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.790
He healed

00:06:24.790 --> 00:06:24.800
her—that

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.110
right there is going to reach

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:29.030
millions.

00:06:34.440 --> 00:06:36.790
So when I see these things

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:40.430
happen today,

00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:42.950
my flesh got a little... I was like,

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.190
'Uh-oh,'because

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:48.550
I've seen what comes.

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:50.510
And the Lord said, 'I'm giving you more

00:06:50.520 --> 00:06:53.350
time. This is time you can pray as the

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:56.750
church stands up and

00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:56.760
prays.'But

00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:58.990
as I saw the alien files being

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.350
released

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:01.870
and people are talking about that,

00:07:01.880 --> 00:07:04.670
the Lord said...

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:07.270
People said, 'Brandon, you said

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:09.590
that after the alien stuff comes out,

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:12.430
it's months later.'I said, 'No, an alien

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:16.430
false

00:07:16.430 --> 00:07:16.440
visitation.'I

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:18.550
didn't say when they start

00:07:18.550 --> 00:07:18.560
talking.

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:20.909
There's going to be

00:07:20.919 --> 00:07:22.670
an encounter,

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:24.310
a fake

00:07:24.320 --> 00:07:28.390
demonic spirit that will look like the

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:29.950
log people

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:33.070
on Guardians of the Galaxy—is what I saw

00:07:33.080 --> 00:07:35.150
interviewing

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:37.670
with a lady.

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:40.630
I saw a demonic spirit, the Nephilim,

00:07:40.640 --> 00:07:42.670
some kind of something.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:44.830
I still don't know all that

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:46.390
I've seen or how to describe

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:48.430
everything I've seen to you,

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:51.510
but it looked like a log creature.

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:53.070
And they were interviewing this

00:07:53.080 --> 00:07:55.710
demonic-looking spirit

00:07:55.720 --> 00:08:01.830
on TV as a great deception.

00:08:01.840 --> 00:08:04.950
There's false demonic encounters that

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:07.830
will deceive the nations

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:10.150
and they will

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:12.630
explain away the rapture of the church

00:08:12.640 --> 00:08:15.110
and where all the Christians went

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.670
because there's going to be millions, over

00:08:17.670 --> 00:08:17.680
a

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:20.790
billion,

00:08:20.800 --> 00:08:22.630
that will be raptured. And I'm

00:08:22.640 --> 00:08:24.310
believing with all my heart that we're

00:08:24.320 --> 00:08:25.950
about to see the greatest harvest of

00:08:25.960 --> 00:08:28.030
souls this world has ever seen before.

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:29.070
Now, there's a lot of people who don't

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.830
believe in the rapture, and that's fine.

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:34.070
I'm not here to

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:36.670
argue theology, but I believe if you

00:08:36.680 --> 00:08:38.390
don't believe it, you're not

00:08:38.390 --> 00:08:38.400
qualified

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:41.110
to go.

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:42.350
You'll be here.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:44.829
Enjoy your tribulation.

00:08:44.839 --> 00:08:47.190
But I do not believe I'm

00:08:47.200 --> 00:08:49.350
appointed unto wrath. I do not believe

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.470
that my God is a wife beater

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.710
and He's not going to beat up on the

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:55.790
bride and bring her to His side.

00:08:57.839 --> 00:09:01.270
Would you beat up your wife?

00:09:01.280 --> 00:09:03.230
No,

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:05.110
you wouldn't, sir. No good

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:06.829
husband

00:09:06.839 --> 00:09:08.829
would.

00:09:08.839 --> 00:09:10.950
Neither would my God beat His

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:12.230
church.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:13.710
You say, 'Well, all these things have

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:13.720
gone

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:15.550
through the church and they've been

00:09:15.560 --> 00:09:19.270
hard times and all this.'We've not seen

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:22.430
on this earth any generation go through

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.630
anything of what we're about to see with

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:27.430
the tribulation.

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:30.590
Your mind can't comprehend what's about

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:33.550
to take place—of the

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:35.750
dispensation of grace coming to an end

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:40.030
and the tribulation to begin.

00:09:40.040 --> 00:09:41.950
People don't understand how bad

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:45.030
tribulation truly is. You're trying to

00:09:45.040 --> 00:09:47.430
say what the disciples went through

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:50.150
and how they went through martyrdom

00:09:50.150 --> 00:09:50.160
compared

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:53.710
to tribulation.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.150
What the disciples went through was

00:09:55.160 --> 00:09:56.750
horrific.

00:09:56.760 --> 00:09:58.750
But I'm trying to tell you, on the vast

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:01.590
scale of how bad tribulation is, you

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.670
don't get it

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:05.630
because no man has ever seen what's

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:07.990
about to happen before

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:10.990
with earthquakes, volcanoes,

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:14.550
pestilence, plagues, wars, and rumors of

00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:16.790
wars. He said that was the beginning of

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:20.870
sorrows in Matthew 24.

00:10:20.880 --> 00:10:22.710
But you all are saying, 'Well, I believe

00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:22.720
it's

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:23.830
going to be

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:27.230
hell on

00:10:27.230 --> 00:10:27.240
earth,'especially

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:28.550
the great tribulation after

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:33.030
the last three and a half years.

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:34.950
But all of it is tribulation, ladies and

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:38.310
gentlemen—seven

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:40.710
years.

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:42.590
But most people say, 'Well,

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:45.190
the disciples went through it.

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:46.750
They went through it in the

00:10:46.760 --> 00:10:48.910
Dark Ages.

00:10:48.920 --> 00:10:50.950
What makes us any

00:10:50.950 --> 00:10:50.960
different?'That

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:55.190
wasn't tribulation.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:58.510
So, we can argue theology all you want,

00:10:58.520 --> 00:11:00.950
but you're never going to convince me

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:03.710
that I'm going to go through any of it.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:05.270
Never will.

00:11:05.280 --> 00:11:06.910
I believe

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:09.590
if you truly knew him

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:11.550
and you sit and talk to him and

00:11:11.560 --> 00:11:13.990
feel his presence

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.630
like I

00:11:15.630 --> 00:11:15.640
do—like

00:11:15.640 --> 00:11:17.270
I know some of the others that I

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:20.310
walk with and my group of

00:11:20.310 --> 00:11:20.320
people—none

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:22.150
of us believe that we're going through

00:11:22.160 --> 00:11:23.670
it.

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:26.110
In fact, I don't know any of the

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:27.630
elders I talk to who believe we're

00:11:27.640 --> 00:11:29.710
going through the tribulation.

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:31.270
None of them.

00:11:31.280 --> 00:11:32.550
They all believe we're out of here

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:34.830
before all that stinky stuff starts to

00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:37.750
happen for the church. But people want

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:39.950
to cleave to what they want to, and they

00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:42.030
grab onto it and believe this. But

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:43.710
this isn't about that.

00:11:43.720 --> 00:11:47.590
This is about the tariffs.

00:11:47.600 --> 00:11:52.270
So, all that to be said, where are we?

00:11:52.280 --> 00:11:54.030
There's a lot

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:56.390
that I have seen

00:11:56.400 --> 00:11:59.510
over the last week and a half that I

00:11:59.520 --> 00:12:03.470
have not been allowed to talk

00:12:03.470 --> 00:12:03.480
about—very

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:07.910
detailed things.

00:12:07.920 --> 00:12:11.390
And the Lord said,

00:12:11.400 --> 00:12:13.510
'You are not going to

00:12:13.520 --> 00:12:15.510
be allowed

00:12:15.520 --> 00:12:17.350
to talk about these things. I want you

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:21.030
to be slow to make content and listen to

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:25.110
me when I tell you to do

00:12:25.110 --> 00:12:25.120
it.'But

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:27.470
I'm speaking and telling you these

